        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2670023860" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13986232918186752218">A well written thriller concerning the mysterious survivors of the Belzec death camp during World War II, and the deadly secret that protects them still 40 years later.<br/><br/>Interesting use of Jewish folklore in a contemporary setting, but reads more like a thriller, or horror lite.<br/><br/>3.5 stars</span>

          </span>
