<li class='cover' id='bookCover_2784797'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2784797-the-reaping"><img alt="The Reaping" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1265745563l/2784797._SX98_.jpg" />
